Package: clintlf
Title: Clinical Trial Table Listing and Figure Utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ki Heun", "Chung", , "khchung0719@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides lightweight, standalone utility functions for preparing
    and formatting clinical reporting outputs, including tables, listings, and
    figures (TLFs). The package does not impose any specific framework,
    package ecosystem, or dependency stack, allowing integration across a wide
    range of R workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/kiheunch/clintlf
BugReports: https://github.com/kiheunch/clintlf/issues
